	</funcsynopsis>
	</refsynopsisdiv>
	<refsect1><title>Description</title>
	    <para>
Returns FcTrue if <parameter>dir</parameter> has an associated valid cache
file, else returns FcFalse
	    </para>
	</refsect1>
    </refentry>
